Anglo American First-Half Underlying EPS Increases 40% to $3.1 Billion

-- B y   J o h n   V i l j o e n
-- 
2011-07-29T06:04:07Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-07-29/anglo-american-first-half-underlying-eps-increases-40-to-3-1-billion.html
Anglo American Plc (AAL)  said first-half
underying earnings increased 40 percent to $3.1 billion, or
$2.58 a share. The company commented in a statement today.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
John Viljoen at 
 jviljoen@bloomberg.net  